<p>Ways to manage poll options:</p>
<ol>
	<li>Create poll options by typing in the name of the poll option and clicking "add to options"</li>
	<li>Rearrange the poll options by selecting them from the list and clicking the up and down arrow options</li>
	<li>Rename/Edit poll options by selecting them from the list and clicking the pencil icon</li>
	<li>Delete poll options by selecting them from the list and clicking the trashcan icon</li>
</ol>
<p>When you're done, make sure you click "save" down below!</p>